Dawn M. Zier to Join Nutrisystem as President and Chief Executive Officer | Business Wire


























































Dawn M. Zier to Join Nutrisystem as President and Chief Executive 
      Officer






Reader’s Digest veteran brings analytics-driven multi-channel 
      marketing approach, turnaround and leadership skills to the top job at 
      Nutrisystem










